      about_city_view: '<strong>City\'s Position:</strong> "Given the declining number of students, there is no time to delay school reorganization — it must be carried out as soon as possible." (Komaki City Board of Education)',
      about_plan_h2: 'Phase 1 Reorganization Plan<small>Phase 1 Reorganization Plan</small>',
      about_plan_intro: 'In FY2027, the current <strong>5 elementary schools and 3 junior high schools</strong> will be reorganized into <strong>2 elementary schools and 2 junior high schools</strong>. Schools are grouped into "East" (Tokadai Higashi) and "West" (Tokadai Nishi).',
