      transport_elem_h: 'Elementary Students: School Bus',
      transport_elem_p: 'A <strong>school bus service is being introduced</strong> for elementary students.<br><br>· <strong>Morning route:</strong> 1 trip<br>· <strong>Afternoon routes:</strong> Up to 3 trips (on days with club activities)<br>· <strong>Cost: Fully covered by the city (free for students)</strong><br><br>Bus stops and schedules will be determined after coordination with schools and operators.',
      transport_jhs_h: 'Junior High Students: Bicycle Commuting',
      transport_jhs_p: '<strong>Bicycle commuting</strong> is planned for junior high students.<br><br>Details regarding safe commuting routes and rainy-day arrangements will be studied and announced at a later date.',
      about_phase2_h2: 'About Phase 2 Reorganization<small>Phase 2 (Future)</small>',
      about_phase2_box: '<strong>Outlook after Phase 1:</strong> If student numbers continue to decline after Phase 1 (FY2027), further consolidation into <strong>1 elementary and 1 junior high school</strong> may be considered, along with the introduction of <strong>integrated elementary-junior high education</strong>. The decision on Phase 2 will be made based on the situation following Phase 1.',
